Package: nanodRop
Title: Tools for Importing and Processing NanoDrop One Spectral Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Beatrice", "Bock", , "bmb646@nau.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2240-9360"))
Description: Provides utilities to import, parse, and convert spectral data files
    exported by the NanoDrop One spectrophotometer into tidy CSV format suitable
    for downstream analysis in R.
Keywords: spectrophotometry, NanoDrop, spectral-data, data-import
